OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Serious deficiencies' in  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBank's economy forecasts   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Bank of England's economic         
OL,6, forecasting system has "serious        
OL,7, deficiencies" that need to be          
OL,8, modernised, according to a review.     
OL,10,FThe independent report by Dr Ben       
OL,11,FBernanke, former head of the US central
OL,12,Fbank, found staff used outdated systems
OL,13,Fthat should be overhauled or replaced. 
OL,15,FHe found there had been serious        
OL,16,Funder-investment in the Bank's         
OL,17,Fsoftware.                              
OL,19,FBut Governor Andrew Bailey said        
OL,20,Fupdating the Bank's systems was a "high
OL,21,Fpriority".                             
